{"tid":939913,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)龍如x中村xHERO 審判之眼","createTime":"2018-12-13T13:25:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T14:19:43.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5239467e452bbec8f2b421d977cb64313b1698a4","tid":939913,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T13:25:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">玩唔完下次播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/thanksyour\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fthanksyour&d=YucF8bmLBH1D1PshIAAR954%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=868c4890\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/thanksyour</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=YucF8bmLBH1D1PshIAAR954%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=ae5ad7e6\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=YucF8bmLBH1D1PshIAAR954%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=c361cc7b\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/0/06/JUDGE_EYES.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F0%2F06%2FJUDGE_EYES.jpg&h=e8a3475e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過去主角八神隆之曾任殺人案嫌疑人大久保新平的辯護律師，當時在輿論極為不利的情況下，漂亮地獲得無罪判決而一時聲名大噪，但當事人被釋放後不久，竟犯下殘殺同居女友並且對住所公寓縱火之罪行，八神的評價因此一落千丈，並且被大眾稱為「縱放兇惡殺人兇手的冒牌律師」，也讓他失去了先前建立的一切聲譽，並自此離開了律師的工作。<br />\n事件3年後，離開律師一行的八神在神室町開設了一家偵探事務所，並以萬事屋的身分餬口，此時一件自源田法律事務接下關於神室町連續殺人事件的委託，開始改變了他的命運<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=YucF8bmLBH1D1PshIAAR954%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=ddb4d773\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=YucF8bmLBH1D1PshIAAR954%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=6b8dadce\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32be15bdc8d7687dd7a71937239fd34f365a64f8","tid":939913,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T13:26:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ceecb9ed2b3737f817f4c03288b98cda0f4e77","tid":939913,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T13:56:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 木村"},{"pid":"7fc64652f462e98edece9ae24de2967a99356002","tid":939913,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T14:19:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}